{"tid":110991,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲Pussy又剷草啦","createTime":"2017-02-07T06:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T07:01:41.000Z","uid":11354,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71abc0666a0df8067dff9cae5273100afc10dec1","tid":110991,"uid":11354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:17:02.000Z","msg":"前阿仙奴球員厄茲亞庫普（Oguzhan Ozyakup），和名將雲佩斯曾是隊友。但日前他卻公開表示，他和雲佩斯不再是朋友了。 <br />\n<br />\n　　雲佩斯在費倫巴治效力，厄茲亞庫普目前在比錫達斯效力。日前，這兩隊之間直接對話，雲佩斯在比賽中攻入一球，入球後他非常興奮，在前隊友厄茲亞庫普身邊滑軌慶祝，這讓後者非常不滿。 <br />\n<br />\n　　厄茲亞庫普表示：「球場上有很多事情，但我不會說它們，不過有一件事是例外，我曾在賽場上有一個很好的朋友，今天之後卻變了，有時候你在球場上才能看清楚一名足球運動員的真面目。」<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JMIstENeZn4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJMIstENeZn4&d=Gknyi0oE%2F3XF1rBdSl6%2FM4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=49acbc2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JMIstENeZn4</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mC-S6TtCspg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmC-S6TtCspg&d=Gknyi0oE%2F3XF1rBdSl6%2FM4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=c1e0db28\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mC-S6TtCspg</a>"},{"pid":"ab7ce7d18d815211dbedece6b458fedb9f604fa2","tid":110991,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:18:51.000Z","msg":"1234"},{"pid":"456f660419c7d203ee5624108f5d6626d131a152","tid":110991,"uid":760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:21:31.000Z","msg":"邊撚個"},{"pid":"a31dbcecd629b10c836274acd19dbefff50c4f13","tid":110991,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:22:45.000Z","msg":"邊銀個"},{"pid":"a589135a4e5ecb577d740a25a7f38b949e641cae","tid":110991,"uid":29916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T06:24:59.000Z","msg":"1234"},{"pid":"eb053ce016145699d303dd1407fcc81647d942b4","tid":110991,"uid":10702,"like":0,"di